Package aspguidc.exception.parsing

  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    DefinitionFormatException
    Signals that the input is not valid according to the graphical user interface definition format.
    InvalidAtomRepresentationTemplateFormatException
    Signals that an atom representation template in the gui definition not a valid.
    InvalidConditionStatementFormatException
    Signals that a condition statement in the gui definition is not valid.
    InvalidIdentifierFormatException
    Signals that an identifier in the gui definition is not valid.
    InvalidJsonObjectException
    Signals that a section of the gui definition is not a valid json object.
    InvalidPropertyTypeException
    Signals that a property of the gui definition has an invalid type.
    InvalidSourceSelectorFormatException
    Signals that a source selector in the gui definition is not valid.
    MissingPropertyException
    Signals that a required property of the gui definition was not found.
    MissingRepresentationTemplatePlaceholderException
    Signals that a placeholder which was used inside a representation template is not defined in the gui definition.
